OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: Taliban ban   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FHelmand barbers from       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftrimming beards            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Taliban have banned hairdressers in
OL,6, Afghanistan's Helmand province from    
OL,7, shaving or trimming beards, saying it  
OL,8, breaches their interpretation of       
OL,9, Islamic law.                           
OL,11,FAnyone violating the rule will be      
OL,12,Fpunished, Taliban religious police say.
OL,14,FSome barbers in the capital Kabul have 
OL,15,Fsaid they also received similar orders.
OL,17,FThe instructions suggest a return to   
OL,18,Fthe strict rulings of the group's past 
OL,19,Ftenure in power, despite promises of a 
OL,20,Fmilder form of government.             
